Afta tri wik , a aks am if i go mared mi , ɛn afta siks wiks wi mared .
Dɛn bin mek mi ɛn Maksin bi mishɔnari na Poto Riko so a nɔ ɛva travul pan di nyu bot .
Fɔ ɛgzampul , na wan vilej we dɛn kɔl Potala Pastilo , tu witnɛs famili dɛn bin de de we gɛt bɔku pikin dɛn ɛn a bin yus fɔ ple flut wit dɛn .
